# Root-level .gitignore
# Each sub-project (pollingapp/, pollingapp-client/) has its own .gitignore
# for language/framework specific patterns.  This file covers repo-wide rules.

# ── Secrets ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# The .env file contains real credentials (DB_PASSWORD, JWT_SECRET).
# .env.example is committed as a template; .env is never committed.
.env
*.env
!.env.example

# ── OS noise ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
docs/
